Add complete SYSFS interface for PCF2131 interrupt control

This patch adds SYSFS attributes for runtime control of PCF2131
interrupt masks and periodic interrupts:

- inta_mask: Read/write INTA interrupt mask register (0x31)
- intb_mask: Read/write INTB interrupt mask register (0x33)  
- minute_interrupt: Enable/disable minute periodic interrupts
- second_interrupt: Enable/disable second periodic interrupts

All interfaces are PCF2131-specific and return -ENOTSUPP for other devices.

Signed-off-by: Dynamic Devices <support@dynamicdevices.co.uk>

